I'm untrusting of what I see presented in the media 
as a major situation. I think that, well, I fear

00:51.060 --> 01:07.281
that in many situations what looks like a major 
demonstration may be just a very small group

00:51.060 --> 01:07.281
making a very large amount of noise. Actually, the 
only personal confrontation I had with Savio and

01:09.860 --> 01:25.264
his followers was, I guess in retrospect, a 
somewhat humorous situation that came up. When I

01:26.466 --> 01:35.260
was at Berkeley working on my doctorate, I did my 
research work at the Lawrence Radiation

01:26.466 --> 01:35.260
Laboratory up on the hill. And it was literally up 
on a hill. It was a long, steep road going up to the

01:37.450 --> 01:41.355
laboratories. At that time, I managed to get back 
and forth between home and the laboratories on a

01:42.075 --> 01:58.294
Vespa motor scooter, which was not the most 
powerful device I've ever had the privilege to

01:42.075 --> 01:58.294
drive around. In order to get to the laboratory on 
the Vespa, I would have to wind it up like a top at the

01:58.814 --> 02:17.039
bottom of the hill and roar with all my heart right 
up to the back door, because if I didn't, if I slowed

01:58.814 --> 02:17.039
down on the way up the hill, I simply couldn't make 
it. I would literally have to get off and push that

02:17.239 --> 02:21.165
brute all the way to the top of the hill. There 
was... One situation when Savio, trying to make

02:24.616 --> 02:44.008
some point, I have not the foggiest notion as to 
what it was at that time, but they decided that they

02:24.616 --> 02:44.008
were going to boycott the Rad Lab, and various 
members of Savio's following most of which,

02:44.309 --> 02:55.941
incidentally, I don't think had any idea as to what 
they were trying to say or what their

02:44.309 --> 02:55.941
demonstration was about. But they blockaded or 
tried to blockade the laboratory, and they did it

02:56.521 --> 03:06.591
by means of setting up effectively human 
barricades on the road. Well, I didn't know what

03:07.372 --> 03:14.299
they were doing, but I came to work one morning, and 
with my usual technique, I wound the Vespa up at the

03:14.633 --> 03:19.801
bottom of the hill, and I was going hell-bent for 
thunder for the top. And here they were, standing

03:20.262 --> 03:23.407
in front of me, waving placards at me. And there was 
no way I was going to push that Vespa all the way to

03:24.168 --> 03:29.256
the top of that hill, so I just kept on going. And I'm 
afraid that Savio's followers ended up thrashing

03:30.078 --> 03:37.590
rather vigorously in the bushes by the time I got 
by. But it's... I didn't really feel like I was

03:40.216 --> 03:50.768
doing the system any real justice. I simply was 
going to work.

