12:16.557 --> 12:22.972
the administration was concerned. He was not, he 
doesn't understand or didn't understand the

12:23.494 --> 12:34.600
potential values of nuclear power. And I think 
that he did the industry as a whole a severe

12:35.187 --> 12:45.106
disservice, principally out of ignorance. And 
that bothers me, that that kind of situation could

12:45.346 --> 12:54.343
cause the damage that it did.

